special_powers.name: MINION: PROUD RACE
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the Kryptonian keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, Kryptonian Scientist can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: BRAINSTORMING FOR WEAPONRY
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the Scientist keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, Kryptonian Scientist can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: EARTH'S YELLOW SUN
special_powers.description: If General Zod is 125 points, he is KO'd when he crosses the red KO line.  If General Zod is 225 points, he is not KO'd when he crosses the red KO line; instead, stop turning the dial and he has "wing symbol" and "indomitable symbol".

special_powers.name: ALL MY TRAINING, ALL HIS POWER
special_powers.description: General Zod can use Quake and Super Strength.  When he does, after actions resolve, you may place him next to a figure that was knocked back and make a close combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: FANATICAL FOLLOWERS
special_powers.description: General Zod can use Mastermind.  When he does, he may deal the damage to any friendly character with a lower point value, within 3 squares and line of fire; if you do, place that character adjacent to General Zod.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD COMMANDER
special_powers.description: General Zod can use Leadership.  When he does and may remove an action token from an adjacent character, he may instead modify that character's attack and damage values +1.

special_powers.name: THE REGIME MUST FALL
special_powers.description: When Kryptonian Rebel targets a character with the Kryptonian keyword and a higher point value with an attack, he can use Willpower and modifies his attack value by +1 this turn.

special_powers.name: CUNNING SCIENTIST
special_powers.description: Jor-El can use Outwit. When he does, he may be given a power action instead of a free action to counter a team ability instead of a power or combat ability.

special_powers.name: BATTLE ARMOR
special_powers.description: Kryptonian Warrior can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Toughness.

special_powers.name: NOSY REPORTER
special_powers.description: Lois Lane can use Outwit; when she does, she ignores characters for line of fire purposes.

special_powers.name: STRENGTH IN NUMBERS
special_powers.description: After Soldier resolves a move action and is adjacent to a friendly character named Soldier, he may be given a close or ranged combat action as a free action.

special_powers.name: TRAVELING THE WORLD
special_powers.description: Clark Kent can use Leap/Climb. When given a move action, modify Clark Kent's speed value by +3.

special_powers.name: HELPING FROM A DISTANCE
special_powers.description: If Clark Kent has not KO'd an opposing character, he can use Stealth; if he has, he can't use Stealth from any game effect.

special_powers.name: DETERMINED TO GET ANSWERS
special_powers.description: Clark Kent can use Toughness and Willpower.

special_powers.name: STRONGEST KRYPTONIAN
special_powers.description: Nam-Ek can use Super Strength. When Nam-Ek is given a move action, you may give him a standard heavy object to hold from outside the game.

special_powers.name: DESTROY FOR GENERAL ZOD
special_powers.description: When Nam-Ek attacks a character with the Superman Ally team ability or the Kryptonian keyword, modify his attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: DEADLY WEAPONS
special_powers.description: Give Jax-Ur a power action, chose an adjacent friendly character, and roll a d6. On a result of 1-4, damage dealt by the chosen character can't be reduced below 1 this turn; 0n a result of 5-6, damage dealt by that character is penetrating damage this turn.

special_powers.name: TO SAVE MY SON
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Superman would be KO'd, you may instead turn him to his last click and KO Lara Lor-Van instead.

special_powers.name: PLANNING AHEAD
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with a lower point value and the Soldier keyword within 8 squares can use Willpower. Give Colonel Hardy a power action; adjacent characters named Superman can use Willpower this turn.

special_powers.name: VISION POWERS
special_powers.description: Faora ignores Stealth.

special_powers.name: JOR-EL'S SERVANT
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters named Jor-El can use Mastermind, but only to deal damage to Kelex, and regardless of their point values.

special_powers.name: BATTLE MODE
special_powers.description: Kelex can use Close Combat Expert.  When turning the dial, if this click is revealed due to damage taken from an opponent's attack, stop turning the dial.

special_powers.name: CONQUEROR
special_powers.description: When General Zod attacks a single opposing character and hits, if that character has 1 action token, give that character a second action token.

special_powers.name: THE MAN OF STEEL
special_powers.description: Superman can use Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: A SUPERMAN FOR ANY SITUATION
special_powers.description: Superman is a wildcard, but may only copy the team abilities of friendly characters with whom he shares a keyword.

special_powers.name: POWERED BY EARTH'S YELLOW SUN
special_powers.description: Superman may use Charge; when he does he may use Improved Movement: Destroy Blocking, Characters

special_powers.name: SOLAR REGENERATION
special_powers.description: Superman can use Regeneration. When he occupies a square of outdoor terrain, you may add the elevation level to the result of the d6 roll.

special_powers.name: AN INSPIRATION
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with a lower point value that begin or end an action adjacent to Superman can use Willpower for that action.

special_powers.name: I'M HERE TO HELP
special_powers.description: Superman can use Defend and Probability Control, but only to replace the defense values and reroll the rolls of characters that are not on their starting click.

special_powers.name: LAB EXPLOSION
special_powers.description: Jor-El can use Pulse Wave. When he does, his damage value becomes 2 and is locked; after actions resolve, deal Jor-El 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: ADVANCE TECHNOLOGY
special_powers.description: Jor-El can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: I SEE A NEW PATH FOR US
special_powers.description: Jor-El can use Outwit and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: FOR KRYPTON
special_powers.description: Kryptonian Warrior modifies his attack and damage value by +1 when attacking a character with the Trio of Doom keyword or Superman Enemy team ability.

special_powers.name: MINION: FIGHTING SPIRIT
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with a higher point value and the Warrior keyword is within 8 squares, Kryptonian Warrior can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: ENRAGED
special_powers.description: Nam-Ek can use Battle Fury and Close Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: ESPIONAGE
special_powers.description: Faora can use Stealth. When Faora is the target of a ranged combat attack, she can use Super Senses.

special_powers.name: MILITARY STRATEGIST
special_powers.description: General Zod can use Leadership and Perplex. He can use Perplex normally, or may target each friendly character within line of fire and with whom he shares a keyword.
